WEBVTT

00:01.315 --> 00:02.875
BOYD:Previously onFrom...

00:06.681 --> 00:08.215
(SHRIEKS)

00:08.315 --> 00:10.215
CHILDREN: Anghkooey.
Anghkooey.

00:10.485 --> 00:12.140
No, no, no, no, no, no!
Anghkooey. Anghkooey.

00:12.240 --> 00:12.835
Don't touch me!
Don't touch me!

00:12.835 --> 00:13.335
Don't, don't. No! Don't!
Anghkooey. Anghkooey.

00:13.335 --> 00:14.805
Don't touch me!
Don't touch me!

00:16.955 --> 00:18.285
Hey! Hey!
You okay?

00:18.405 --> 00:21.135
Did you see them?
See what? See who?

00:22.455 --> 00:24.075
JIM: We heard a voice
on the radio.

00:24.225 --> 00:27.015
He knew my name.
Knew what my wife
was doin' in the house.

00:27.015 --> 00:29.433
In the basement.
Jim...

00:29.735 --> 00:31.085
I think people
are watching us.

00:31.095 --> 00:33.075
We've gotta start
working together on this.

00:33.165 --> 00:34.095
I gotta go, Jim.

00:35.475 --> 00:38.325
KRISTI:You were
on your way to rehab
and you ended up here.

00:38.355 --> 00:39.585
Did you take
anything from here?

00:39.625 --> 00:41.129
It was just a little
bit of morphine so I...

00:41.195 --> 00:41.535
Marielle.

00:42.085 --> 00:44.985
Yeah, fine. Do whatever
the fuck you want!

00:45.955 --> 00:46.725
(MUSIC BOX PLAYING)
MARTIN: They're coming.

00:47.475 --> 00:49.395
You have to get out
before the music stops.

00:49.841 --> 00:50.808
(GASPS)

00:50.908 --> 00:52.041
(SCREAMS)

00:52.141 --> 00:53.708
(STRUGGLING)

00:53.835 --> 00:54.405
My blood...

00:54.735 --> 00:55.785
"...is your blood now."

00:56.445 --> 00:58.685
Look, I got worms
under my skin,

00:58.685 --> 01:01.055
and it feels like
something's coming
for me now.

01:01.685 --> 01:03.095
We can't have
new people

01:03.095 --> 01:04.895
stealing what little
food we have!

01:04.895 --> 01:05.758
Get outside!

01:05.758 --> 01:06.634
Dale, come on.

01:06.635 --> 01:07.728
Get off me!
No!

01:07.802 --> 01:09.235
(PEOPLE GASPING)

01:09.335 --> 01:11.169
(KNOCKING)
ELGIN AND FATIMA: Help!

01:12.175 --> 01:13.368
Boyd! Kenny!
I'm gonna need you
up here!

01:13.467 --> 01:15.405
ELLIS: I can't breathe!
Breathe in again.

01:15.925 --> 01:16.555
FATIMA: Kristi,
what's happening?

01:16.818 --> 01:19.118
I'm gonna relieve
the pressure, all right?

01:19.118 --> 01:20.185
(GASPS)

01:20.185 --> 01:22.188
You can't put
my blood into him.
Boyd...

01:22.287 --> 01:25.365
Whatever's inside me
is going to go into him!

01:25.375 --> 01:26.025
Boyd!
Boyd!

01:26.442 --> 01:27.475
BOYD:I got an idea.

01:27.575 --> 01:29.042
(GRUNTS)

01:30.625 --> 01:34.823
My blood
is your blood now,
motherfucker.

01:34.823 --> 01:37.657
(SCREAMS)

01:42.305 --> 01:43.675
I almost lost him!

01:44.035 --> 01:45.475
But you didn't, okay?

01:46.285 --> 01:47.935
I need to ask
you something.

01:48.535 --> 01:49.495
Yeah, of course.

01:51.525 --> 01:53.515
Do you have
any pregnancy tests?

01:59.985 --> 02:01.035
Are you sure?

02:01.975 --> 02:05.625
As sure as I can be,
given the circumstances.

02:07.825 --> 02:09.355
Have you said
anything to Ellis yet?

02:09.789 --> 02:10.755
(EXHALES SHAKILY)

02:10.755 --> 02:14.095
Uh, no, no, not...
not yet, I, uh...

02:14.965 --> 02:17.785
I know these
aren't the most
ideal conditions,

02:17.785 --> 02:21.505
but women have
been giving birth
for thousands of years.

02:21.985 --> 02:22.555
Right.

02:23.965 --> 02:25.135
And...

02:26.755 --> 02:28.315
not all of them have

02:28.315 --> 02:30.565
a third-year medical student
to guide them through.

02:31.645 --> 02:33.565
Look, talk to Ellis,
the three of us can...

02:33.655 --> 02:34.705
I can't. I...

02:35.012 --> 02:37.015
I don't want to say
anything to him yet.

02:37.678 --> 02:39.178
(KNOCKING)

02:40.315 --> 02:41.815
Hey, sun's coming up.

02:41.815 --> 02:43.255
KRISTI: Yeah.
We'll be right there.

02:44.555 --> 02:45.505
Fatima, what's going on?

02:47.521 --> 02:48.855
Fatima...
We should go.

02:49.805 --> 02:50.605
Sorry. We should go.

03:08.075 --> 03:08.645
All right.

03:16.935 --> 03:17.585
You good?

03:42.075 --> 03:43.005
KRISTI: Jesus.

03:44.895 --> 03:45.795
You really did it.

03:47.775 --> 03:48.825
You killed one of them.

03:50.935 --> 03:52.165
What do we do
with the body?

03:53.455 --> 03:54.415
We should burn it.

03:54.955 --> 03:55.555
BOYD: No.

03:57.315 --> 03:58.365
We take it inside.

03:59.955 --> 04:01.335
Tell me
you're joking.

04:01.635 --> 04:03.075
KRISTI: No,
he's right. This is...

04:03.075 --> 04:04.815
This is our chance
to learn about them.

04:05.325 --> 04:06.855
We could study them,
open them up,

04:06.885 --> 04:08.715
see what they look
like on the inside.

04:08.973 --> 04:10.995
We... we don't even
know if it's safe
to touch this thing!

04:10.995 --> 04:13.545
You're talking about...
about operating on it!

04:15.985 --> 04:16.615
You guys...

04:18.051 --> 04:19.251
BOYD: Kristi.

04:19.865 --> 04:20.344
It's your call.

04:22.535 --> 04:23.345
Let's bring it in.

04:24.575 --> 04:25.535
MARIELLE:
I'll get a sheet.

04:25.715 --> 04:26.795
We can drag it.

04:28.925 --> 04:29.255
(KENNY SCOFFS)
Thanks.

04:30.035 --> 04:31.145
I'll grab some sticks.

04:31.175 --> 04:34.085
Ellis. I need you
to head back up
to Colony House.

04:36.065 --> 04:37.265
No, I wanna stay.

04:37.815 --> 04:39.935
Yeah, you do that,
we're gonna have
dozens of people

04:39.935 --> 04:42.545
comin' to check on you,
and we gotta keep this quiet.

04:43.415 --> 04:45.095
At least until
we have a chance
to get a look at it.

04:46.115 --> 04:48.657
Hey, uh, Kristi,
are you good
if we head back?

04:48.756 --> 04:50.765
I mean, yeah,
but you gotta
take it easy.

04:50.795 --> 04:52.535
You come back to me
immediately

04:52.535 --> 04:54.215
if you have any trouble
breathing, okay?

04:54.605 --> 04:57.095
Keep the bandage nice and dry,
and I'll check on you later.

04:57.815 --> 04:59.345
Okay.
'Kay?

04:59.345 --> 04:59.915
Let's go.
Yeah.

04:59.915 --> 05:00.275
Elgin.

05:00.875 --> 05:01.415
Yeah?

05:04.225 --> 05:04.455
What?

05:05.365 --> 05:06.295
You all right?

05:08.715 --> 05:09.135
I'm fine.

05:12.435 --> 05:13.455
Be careful.

05:13.815 --> 05:14.655
Yeah. Always.

05:19.682 --> 05:20.715
(EXHALES)

05:22.475 --> 05:22.835
Let's go.

05:24.275 --> 05:24.905
KENNY: You guys.

05:25.413 --> 05:27.465
All right, can we pl...
can we please just stop

05:27.465 --> 05:29.055
and talk about
this for a second?

05:29.905 --> 05:31.045
Kenny, what is there
to talk about?

05:33.925 --> 05:37.825
You're about to
willingly bring something
evil into your home!

05:38.785 --> 05:40.045
Do you understand that?

05:40.525 --> 05:42.295
I do. I also understand

05:42.295 --> 05:44.185
that we may
never get this
opportunity again.

05:44.185 --> 05:45.055
So is that it?

05:46.885 --> 05:47.335
Okay?

05:48.651 --> 05:49.651
(SCOFFS)

05:53.965 --> 05:54.565
All right.
Let's go.

